  "description": "A vibrant orange poppy stands tall amidst a field of green grasses and foliage. The poppy is in full bloom, showcasing delicate, papery petals that transition from a deep orange at the base to a lighter, golden-yellow towards the edges. The stem is slender and green, supporting the flower head. Surrounding the poppy are various shades of green grasses and leaves, creating a natural and textured background. The image has a shallow depth of field, blurring the distant foliage and highlighting the poppy as the central focus. The lighting appears to be natural daylight, casting soft shadows and enhancing the colors.",
